videos.description: Anthony Davis records 12 points and 8 rebounds as he gets back into the groove against the Celtics in Boston.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NBA Highlight (AD gets off to hot start in return vs. Celtics) 2021/01/30 ESHEET SOTFULL

videos.headline: AD gets off to hot start in return vs. Celtics

videos.description: LeBron James draws the contact as he finesses his way to the basket for a smooth and-1 finish to give the Lakers a 51-49 lead over the Celtics.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (LeBron makes sweet and-1 layup before the half) 2021/01/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: LeBron makes sweet and-1 layup before the half

videos.description: Jayson Tatum goes all-out to keep the ball in bounds and flips a pass behind his back to Robert Williams III for the easy finish on the break.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Tatum makes incredible save, Williams gets the finish) 2021/01/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Tatum makes incredible save, Williams gets the finish

videos.description: Marcus Smart falls to the ground in pain and is helped off the floor after attempting to block a shot by Montrezl Harrell.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Smart goes down with apparent leg injury) 2021/01/30 ESHEET

videos.headline: Smart goes down with apparent leg injury

videos.description: The Celtics come up with a steal in the final moments of the game, but fail to convert as the Lakers go on to win 96-95 in Boston.
